{
  "stem": "24814.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She said, don't tell them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Don't tell them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was still so afraid, you know, because the Vichy French were as antisemitic as the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She kept saying, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember the young French doctor-- they're all bilingual, Alsatians-- said, gee, you speak good German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said, yeah, learned it in school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said, you two got a big secret.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, big secret.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We'll never-- she didn't want them to know she was Jewish, even after--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, from them anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she'd hidden out in this house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was the last Jew in Herrlisheim [INAUDIBLE] Colmar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The others were all killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Little old lady.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we went to reserve.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pick up tanks, replace infantry, casualties, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we were in reserve for a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we went on a night march up through Luxembourg to Third Army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Third Army was Patton, the much-advertised Patton's army on our left flank.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were the veterans, and Seventh Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what happened was the Sauer-Moselle Triangle flows into the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Rhine makes kind of a loop, a curve toward the west.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It starts in Switzerland, flows north, then turns northwest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Moselle flows into it, and so there's a big trapezoid formed from the south.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's called the Sauer Basin-- a big industrial area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Germans had their Siegfried Line forts all along the front of it, which we'd been battering against.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the Third Army on our left had broken through the Siegfried Line, was all way up the Moselle to the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the flank was open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they loaned our division to Third Army.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
